{"idRevelationType":"Mekah","idNameTranslation":"Bermuka Masam","number":80,"name":"سورة عبس","englishName":"Abasa","englishNameTranslation":"He frowned","revelationType":"Meccan","numberOfAyahs":42,"ayahs":[{"number":5759,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5759","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5759.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5759.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","latin":"'Abasa wa tawallaa.","en":"The Prophet frowned and turned away","id":"Dia (Muhammad) bermuka masam dan berpaling,"},"numberInSurah":1,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5760,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5760","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5760.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5760.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلْأَعْمَىٰ","latin":"An jaa-ahul 'a-maa","en":"Because there came to him the blind man, [interrupting].","id":"karena telah datang seorang buta kepadanya."},"numberInSurah":2,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5761,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5761","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5761.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5761.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"وَمَا يُدْرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","latin":"Wa maa yudreeka la'allahu yaz zakkaa.","en":"But what would make you perceive, [O Muhammad], that perhaps he might be purified","id":"Tahukah kamu barangkali ia ingin membersihkan dirinya (dari dosa),"},"numberInSurah":3,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5762,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5762","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5762.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5762.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"أَوْ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكْرَىٰٓ","latin":"Au yaz zak karu fatanfa 'ahuz zikraa.","en":"Or be reminded and the remembrance would benefit him?","id":"atau dia (ingin) mendapatkan pengajaran, lalu pengajaran itu memberi manfaat kepadanya?"},"numberInSurah":4,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5763,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5763","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5763.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5763.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسْتَغْنَىٰ","latin":"Amma manis taghnaa","en":"As for he who thinks himself without need,","id":"Adapun orang yang merasa dirinya serba cukup,"},"numberInSurah":5,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5764,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5764","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5764.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5764.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","latin":"Fa-anta lahu tasaddaa","en":"To him you give attention.","id":"maka kamu melayaninya."},"numberInSurah":6,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5765,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5765","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5765.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5765.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"وَمَا عَلَيْكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","latin":"Wa ma 'alaika allaa yaz zakka.","en":"And not upon you [is any blame] if he will not be purified.","id":"Padahal tidak ada (celaan) atasmu kalau dia tidak membersihkan diri (beriman)."},"numberInSurah":7,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5766,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5766","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5766.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5766.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسْعَىٰ","latin":"Wa amma man jaa-aka yas'a","en":"But as for he who came to you striving [for knowledge]","id":"Dan adapun orang yang datang kepadamu dengan bersegera (untuk mendapatkan pengajaran),"},"numberInSurah":8,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5767,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5767","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5767.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5767.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"وَهُوَ يَخْشَىٰ","latin":"Wahuwa yakhshaa,","en":"While he fears [Allah],","id":"sedang ia takut kepada (Allah),"},"numberInSurah":9,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5768,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5768","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5768.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5768.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"فَأَنتَ عَنْهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","latin":"Fa-anta 'anhu talah haa.","en":"From him you are distracted.","id":"maka kamu mengabaikannya."},"numberInSurah":10,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5769,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5769","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5769.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5769.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذْكِرَةٌۭ","latin":"Kalla innaha tazkirah","en":"No! Indeed, these verses are a reminder;","id":"Sekali-kali jangan (demikian)! Sesungguhnya ajaran-ajaran Tuhan itu adalah suatu peringatan,"},"numberInSurah":11,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5770,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5770","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5770.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5770.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","latin":"Faman shaa a zakarah","en":"So whoever wills may remember it.","id":"maka barangsiapa yang menghendaki, tentulah ia memperhatikannya,"},"numberInSurah":12,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5771,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5771","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5771.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5771.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"فِى صُحُفٍۢ مُّكَرَّمَةٍۢ","latin":"Fi suhufim mukar rama,","en":"[It is recorded] in honored sheets,","id":"di dalam kitab-kitab yang dimuliakan,"},"numberInSurah":13,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5772,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5772","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5772.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5772.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"مَّرْفُوعَةٍۢ مُّطَهَّرَةٍۭ","latin":"Marfoo'atim mutah hara,","en":"Exalted and purified,","id":"yang ditinggikan lagi disucikan,"},"numberInSurah":14,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5773,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5773","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5773.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5773.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"بِأَيْدِى سَفَرَةٍۢ","latin":"Bi'aidee safara","en":"[Carried] by the hands of messenger-angels,","id":"di tangan para penulis (malaikat),"},"numberInSurah":15,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5774,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5774","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5774.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5774.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"كِرَامٍۭ بَرَرَةٍۢ","latin":"Kiraamim bararah.","en":"Noble and dutiful.","id":"yang mulia lagi berbakti."},"numberInSurah":16,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5775,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5775","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5775.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5775.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"قُتِلَ ٱلْإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكْفَرَهُۥ","latin":"Qutilal-insanu maa akfarah.","en":"Cursed is man; how disbelieving is he.","id":"Binasalah manusia; alangkah amat sangat kekafirannya?"},"numberInSurah":17,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5776,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5776","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5776.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5776.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"مِنْ أَىِّ شَىْءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","latin":"Min aiyyi shai-in Khalaq","en":"From what substance did He create him?","id":"Dari apakah Allah menciptakannya?"},"numberInSurah":18,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5777,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5777","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5777.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5777.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"مِن نُّطْفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","latin":"Min nutfah; khalaqahu faqad-darah.","en":"From a sperm-drop He created him and destined for him;","id":"Dari setetes mani, Allah menciptakannya lalu menentukannya."},"numberInSurah":19,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5778,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5778","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5778.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5778.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","latin":"Thummas sabeela yas-sarah","en":"Then He eased the way for him;","id":"Kemudian Dia memudahkan jalannya."},"numberInSurah":20,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5779,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5779","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5779.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5779.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقْبَرَهُۥ","latin":"Thumma amatahu fa-aqbarah","en":"Then He causes his death and provides a grave for him.","id":"kemudian Dia mematikannya dan memasukkannya ke dalam kubur,"},"numberInSurah":21,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5780,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5780","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5780.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5780.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","latin":"Thumma iza shaa-a ansharah","en":"Then when He wills, He will resurrect him.","id":"kemudian bila Dia menghendaki, Dia membangkitkannya kembali."},"numberInSurah":22,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5781,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5781","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5781.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5781.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقْضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","latin":"Kalla lamma yaqdi maa amarah.","en":"No! Man has not yet accomplished what He commanded him.","id":"Sekali-kali jangan; manusia itu belum melaksanakan apa yang diperintahkan Allah kepadanya,"},"numberInSurah":23,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5782,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5782","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5782.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5782.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"فَلْيَنظُرِ ٱلْإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","latin":"Falyanzuril insanu ilaa ta-amih","en":"Then let mankind look at his food -","id":"maka hendaklah manusia itu memperhatikan makanannya."},"numberInSurah":24,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5783,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5783","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5783.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5783.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"أَنَّا صَبَبْنَا ٱلْمَآءَ صَبًّۭا","latin":"Anna sabab nalmaa-a sabba.","en":"How We poured down water in torrents,","id":"Sesungguhnya Kami benar-benar telah mencurahkan air (dari langit),"},"numberInSurah":25,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5784,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5784","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5784.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/ar.alafasy/5784.mp3"],"text":{"arab":"ثُمَّ شَقَقْنَا ٱلْأَرْضَ شَقًّۭا","latin":"Thumma sha qaqnal-arda shaqqa.","en":"Then We broke open the earth, splitting [it with sprouts],","id":"kemudian Kami belah bumi dengan sebaik-baiknya,"},"numberInSurah":26,"juz":30,"manzil":7,"page":585,"ruku":522,"hizbQuarter":234,"sajda":false},{"number":5785,"audio":"https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5785","audioSecondary":["https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5785.mp3","https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/64/a